A cyberpunk-style digital workspace floating in neon-lit cyberspace, featuring a glowing holographic mind map with five interconnected nodes branching outward in organic, tree-like patterns. Each node pulses with different neon colors—electric blue, hot pink, toxic green, amber, and violet—connected by streams of flowing data particles. The central hub radiates energy like a digital lotus flower, with intricate circuit-board patterns visible within each branch. The background shows a dark void with distant grid lines stretching to infinity, occasional floating geometric shapes, and rain-like streams of light falling in the distance. The overall composition suggests organized complexity and mastery, with the mind map appearing as a powerful tool for navigating vast digital knowledge. Reflective surfaces catch the neon glow, creating depth and atmosphere.
